dialogueTree.title: Titus Hardie: ""The Stormers can't play for shit.""
Titus Hardie: ""I just let him have it. Left, righ..."
dialogueTree.english: "I just let him have it. Left, right, lights out."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie żałowałem mu. Lewy, prawy i gleba”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Не шкадаваў яго. Левы, правы і зямля".

dialogueTree.title: Titus Hardie: ""Some tits you just have to see to..."
dialogueTree.english: "Some tits you just have to see to believe."
dialogueTree.polish: „Niektóre cycki trzeba zobaczyć, żeby w nie uwierzyć”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Некаторыя цыцкі трэба ўбачыць, каб у іх паверыць".

dialogueTree.title: Titus Hardie: ""Drink up, boys. Social democracy's..."
Titus Hardie: ""Fuck no, beer makes me a *better*..."
dialogueTree.english: "Fuck no, beer makes me a *better* driver."
dialogueTree.polish: „A gdzie tam! Piwo sprawia, że jestem *lepszym* kierowcą”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "А дзе там! Піва робіць мяне *лепшым* кіроўцам".

dialogueTree.title: Titus Hardie: ""Say 'hi' to your momma for me.""
Titus Hardie: ""You need to see that choke-hold ag..."
dialogueTree.english: "You need to see that choke-hold again?"
dialogueTree.polish: „Pokazać ci ten chwyt duszący jeszcze raz?”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Паказаць табе гэты задушлівы прыём яшчэ раз?"

dialogueTree.title: Titus Hardie: ""Though boys... I knew Glen's a bea..."
dialogueTree.english: "Though boys... I knew Glen's a beast, but even Angie..."
dialogueTree.polish: „Twarde chłopaki... Wiedziałem, że Glen to bestia, ale nawet Angie...”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Трывалыя хлопцы... Ведаў, што Глен — звер, але нават Анджы..."

dialogueTree.title: Titus Hardie: ""I'm gonna miss those guys. Theo to..."
dialogueTree.english: "I'm gonna miss those guys. Theo too."
dialogueTree.polish: „Będzie mi brakowało tych chłopaków. Thea też”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Буду сумаваць па гэтых хлопцах. Таксама і па Тэі".

dialogueTree.title: Titus Hardie: ""Fucking good to be alive though.""
Titus Hardie: ""All *we* need to do right now is g..."
dialogueTree.english: "All *we* need to do right now is get our brewskie on."
dialogueTree.polish: „Jedyne, co teraz *musimy*, to dostać nasze browary”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Единнае, што цяпер *павінны*, гэта атрымаць нашыя бровары".
